      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont think it's just fatigue though. it's not like i'm just tired and need a nap. i feel like the person who actually mattered is just... gone. gone for good. and this thing left behind is just taking up space. it feels more like an empty suit than a person.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
