    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's what i'm saying. there is no spark. there's nothing to reignite. its just a hollow vessel that keeps breathing and eating and walking around, but the essence is gone. it feels less like a tragedy and more like a mistake... like something that should have been finished years ago. just a remnant that doesn't belong anymore.",
